# Logo Typography (Locked)

The user has finalized logo font sizes. **Never change these values** when syncing from Figma, matching designs, or refactoring the logo.

## Locked values in `src/constants/brand.ts`

- `productFontSize`: **16** (Deal Builder)
- `taglineFontSize`: **12** (Oakwood showroom finance tool)

## Rules

- Do NOT copy Figma literal font sizes (e.g. 14.769px, 9px) into `brandConfig.figma`
- Do NOT change `productFontSize` or `taglineFontSize` unless the user explicitly requests new sizes
- Figma sync may update layout (logo width/height, gaps, colors) but NOT typography sizes
- If asked to "match Figma pixel-perfect", explain that typography is intentionally overridden for browser readability
